List of proficinceis

a proficiency HAS a list of weapon properties
a weapon property MAY have a list of combat abilities


proficiency -> [weapon properties] ->
	weapon_property -> [combat abilities]

Combat ability is like a spell - you can purchase multiple times (for the same build point cost) they are single use like spells.

{"proficienties": [{"long_crusing": ["armor_destroyer": ["helm_crusher"]]}}
